long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
* Due to Wordle being bought by the NYT, we can now only offer wordle-like games.*

Let's get Wordle adds the popular game-variants of Wordle to your new tab page, helping you never miss a day. 

We are not affiliated with Wordle or https://www.powerlanguage.co.uk in any way.
